      "content": "yeah, a trap. exactly. it feels like there's no way to actually break it. no matter what i change or who i talk to, i just wake up the next day and i'm right back here. it’s like the loop is the only thing that's real. i feel like the only way to actually stop the cycle is to just... stop everything.",
